title: #267 - Kelsey Cook, Taylor Tomlinson, Delanie Fischer, & ME
description:
I sit down in the mancave with the girls of the "Self-Helpless" Podcast Kelsey Cook, Taylor Tomlinson and Delanie Fischer to talk about the me too movement, writing comedy, and sex stories.
